Net::Shaper version 0.3
=======================

Net::Shaper is a simple TCP network traffic shaper.  It acts as a bandwidth-limited
tunnel between a TCP client and a TCP server.  It is written to accept multiple
connections and limit the total bandwidth.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  IO::Select
  Time::HiRes

